An inexplicable discovery in Italy: the missing painting 'Portrait of a Woman' turned up again, not far from the gallery where it was once exhibited! Reveal as a team of investigators the most spectacular art theft in criminal history!

What starts as a 'harmless' burglary gradually turns out to be something much bigger. The discovery of a hidden family secret lies shrouded in mystery. Can you uncover it? Hopefully the clues won't literally get lost in the sand...

The world is in an unprecedented state of emergency. Everyone has to deal with these new challenges. What does this mean? See for yourself by embarking on this 'puzzling' quest filled with adventure and danger, along the way.

Ihr seid auf einer Urlaubsreise und wollt die unberührte Natur genießen. Auf einem Ausflug entdeckt ihr ein Gebäude, völlig überwuchert und anscheinend seit Jahren verlassen. Ihr beschliesst euch die Sache genauer anzusehen und findet eine Tür. Sie lässt sich öffnen. Dieser Einladung folgend betretet Ihr das Gebäude - es scheint ein altes Kraftwerk zu sein. Doch das Gebäude ist nicht so tot wie es scheint. Die Falle schnappt zu…

Tief im Dschungel ist Professor Cortés bei seiner Expedition zum Schatz des Azteken Montezuma verschollen. Der erfahrene Forscher war auf der Suche nach den Überresten des Totenkults, als auf einmal die Verbindung zur Aussenwelt abriß.

Ihr spielt eine Gruppe von vier Freunden, die sich bereits seit ihrer Kindheit kennen und schon damals ein Faible für das Mysteriöse und Ungelöste hatten. Eines lauwarmen sommerlichen Tages trefft ihr euch zu eurem gemeinsamen, wöchentlichen Spielenachmittag. Doch euch ist noch nicht bewusst, dass diesmal nicht alle erscheinen werden.In diesem Spiel werdet Ihr euch in zwei Gruppen aufteilen, die sich gegenseitig unterstützen und stets zusammenarbeiten müssen, um die gemeinsamen Rätsel zu lösen.

You and your team start a new adventure. You enter a fantastic place with an incredible story. A surreal, crazy, nerve-wracking journey through a world full of puzzles, tricks and oddities begins.

New York, 1932. Organized crime is at its peak. You are agents and have been assigned to the case of Vito Genovese. While working on the case, the phone rings. A soft voice whispers: „They know about the photos. They are coming!“. You know that your boss, Joe Petrosino, possesses incriminating material against Don Vito which he keeps well hidden in his office. Can you find and secure the documents before the mafia arrives?

The time is near! You are about to become real witches and wizards. But first, you have to take one final exam. According to tradition, it is held deep in the forest, in the secret hut of the ancient and wise witch. Divination, Broom Flight, Transfiguration – show that you master the magic arts and pass all the assignments in just 60 minutes. Hurry up, the sand is running down the hourglass!

Next to our Escape Room, there is a small watchmaker’s shop. The owner, Regina Jürgensen, appears to be a quiet and unassuming person. But then why are there these strange and sometimes alarmingly loud noises coming from her shop? We would very much appreciate your help in finding out.

A key, an old postcard and a strange note: that’s all Katharina has to find her missing father. Follow his trail through the winding streets of Wernigerode, discover hidden places and solve a decades-old mystery!

Rumour has it that there’s a number of magical creatures living in the Harz region. Is this true or just a myth? Equipped with a mysterious backpack and the notes of a renowned scientist called Prof. Magnus, you start your journey through town in search of these small miraculous beasts.
For all fans of Harry Potter and other magicians. We equip you with a wand and you dive into our magic school.
Dare to enter our Gruselhütte. It's storming outside and half of you were kidnapped. Find together in the room and solve the riddle of the Gruselhütte. Can you appease the ghosts and free yourself?

"I'm looking for someone who will join me on an adventure," Gandalf said to Bilbo in the films. Now start your own ring adventure. Take the One Ring and try to throw it into the volcano at the end of this adventure. Will you succeed or will you fall prey to the ring?
